name: Fruit And Vegetable Tagine
ingredientLines: Ingredients 1 large onion, peeled 2 tbsp olive oil 2 garlic cloves, crushed 1 tsp ground coriander ½ tsp ground ginger ½ tsp ground saffron 400g canned tomatoes, chopped 400ml water or vegetable stock 400g sweet potato or butternut squash, chopped 8 baby carrots, peeled 8 green olives, cracked 8 dried apricots or figs 8 dates (stoned) 1 tsp harissa or chilli sauce 1 tbsp runny honey sea salt and pepper 2 cinnamon sticks 400g zucchini, roughly chopped
